 Girl with the Dragon Tattoo (2011). She resides in Los Angeles with her husband and daughter.","name":"Christine Adams","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Christine Adams (14 de agosto de 1974) es una actriz británica. Es conocida por interpretar a Jessica en Batman Begins (2005), Lena Boudreaux en The Whole Truth (2010-2011) y Lynn Pierce en Black Lightning (2018-2021).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"크리스틴 애덤스","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"クリスティーン・アダムス","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"克莉絲汀·亞當斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"克里斯汀·亚当斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BY","iso_639_1":"be","name":"беларуская мова","english_name":"Belarusian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Крысцін Адамс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"克里斯汀·亞當斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"Κριστίν Άνταμς","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"คริสติน อดัมส์","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Крістін Адамс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Кристин Адамс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"کریستین